{"tid":2306585,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鄭月娥送兩個仔中 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-11-30T13:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T13:58:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9aac34247c6778712ebc8d212b812aa620d68d","tid":2306585,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201130/ZK5PUC5ZLJH7VFC3UH2ROX2RAY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201130%2FZK5PUC5ZLJH7VFC3UH2ROX2RAY%2F&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xOisLzr3S4L08%2B1QJ77HZeU%3D&h=efeee0a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201130%2FZK5PUC5ZLJH7VFC3UH2ROX2RAY%2F&h=12dfebc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201130/ZK5PUC5ZLJH7VFC3UH2ROX2RAY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥送兩個仔中 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6t_eBe4NGC1jtWK8pTddz-0ErSo=/5307x3538/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7FYFAHNRTNGVDH2PUHA7DH2AK4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6t_eBe4NGC1jtWK8pTddz-0ErSo%3D%2F5307x3538%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7FYFAHNRTNGVDH2PUHA7DH2AK4.JPG&h=7a93d68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死因庭罕見的讚美，我們的眼淚又再湧出來，感慨明明穿同一道袍，死因裁判官往往比其他同行講公理、重人倫。當17歲的義務急救員曾朗軒作供完畢，法官大讚他的專業知識，更一錘定音代表周梓樂父母感謝，「你當時照顧得梓樂好好。」周父與朗軒步出法庭，互相拍背鼓勵，鏡頭下的年輕人靦腆，周父面露寬慰。這麼和煦的畫面並不是必然的。我們痛心記得梓樂犧牲後的理大圍城，當晚打算撤離的FA遭防暴反鎖雙手迫令一個貼一個坐在地上，「手足無措」的FA隊員不少是跟梓樂與朗軒差不多的年輕人，當晚救助了多少人？見過多少骨折頭破血流？那個曾經被TG燒傷背脊留下恐怖傷疤的少年FA，在場嗎？<br />\n<br />\n年輕人犧牲夠大了，鄭月娥竟然厚顏說好鍾意年輕人。。。。。。。。。。"}]}